Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.core
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.graph

Interface OntologyGraphEdge<T>

Type Parameters:
T - type of the OntologyGraph node.
All Known Implementing Classes:
Relationship
public interface OntologyGraphEdge<T>
OntologyGraphEdge represents a relation between two OntologyGraph nodes.

The edge is directed and thanks to its directionality, the edge can be read as a triple subject-predicate-object where the relationType() is used as a predicate.

IMPORTANT: The implementor must ensure an appropriate implementation of equals(Object) and hashCode()!

Author:
Daniel Danis
